# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Deployed contract addresses — Chiliz Spicy Testnet (chainId 88882)
# Source: apps/smart-contracts/chiliz-tv/deployments/chilizTestnet.json
# All addresses lowercased on purpose: viem rejects mixed-case non-EIP-55
# strings client-side, lowercase always parses safely.
#
# Mirror with `apps/backend/.env.example` — bump both files in lockstep
# when any deployed address changes (CLAUDE.md §7.11).
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

NEXT_PUBLIC_PARI_MATCH_FACTORY_ADDRESS=0xbba7f5d1ae23ec476d71d24521a39536b9ec8a2f
